Lilah Monroe has spent the last five years playing it safe. After her abusive, controlling relationship comes to end, she swears never to let anyone get close again. With a friend count of two and a mostly introverted life, she feels safe in the bubble she's surrounded her self in. She's happy to live the simple life and she as determined not to let anything change that..until she met him.Hudson Feight used to be adored by fans across the globe, but when the press get hold of a story that paints a very different picture of the man that everyone loves, the adoration soon turns to hatred. For six months he's been hiding away from the world, refusing to let anyone but his manager and his bandmates see his face. He drinks the day away and barely leaves his room.He's done with the band..He's done with women..He's done with life....until he meets her.